<l>pullik kiṭantēṉ puṭaipeyarntē ṉavvaḷavi </l>
<l>laḷḷikkoḷ vaṟṟē pacappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I who was in close embrace just turned aside and the moment I did so, sallowness came on me like something to be seized on.</l>
